@page "/inventory"
@attribute [Authorize]

<PageTitle>WMS - Inventory</PageTitle>

<div class="dashboard-header" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 6px 0; color: var(--text-main);">Inventory</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; font-size: 15px;">Real-time stock ledger, physical locations, and adjustments audit trail</p>
</div>

<div style="background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--card-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px;">
    <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">Stock Overview</h3>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">This module is part of <strong>Phase 3: Inventory & Stock Management</strong>. Real-time ledger queries, stock movements list, and stock adjustments approvals will be handled in this section.</p>
</div>
